        <div class="container">
            <div class="case-content-grid gsap-fade-up">
                <div class="case-intro">
                    <h2>Overview</h2>
                    <p style="color:var(--text-muted); font-size:1.1rem;">The Valtra Smart Display is the primary digital interface in Valtra’s newest tractor generation. It brings machine data, settings, guidance and implement control together in one cohesive HMI.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="case-details">
                    <h4>Role & Responsibilities</h4>
                    <p style="color:var(--text-muted);">Complete UI design (logic, flows), Visual system, Iconography, 3D content, Menu architecture.</p>

                    <h4>Challenges</h4>
                    <p style="color:var(--text-muted);">Limited graphics capabilities, strict performance constraints, and integration with physical SmartTouch controls.</p>

                    <h4>Outcome</h4>
                    <p style="color:var(--text-muted);">Contributed to Red Dot, iF Design, and Good Design awards.</p>
                </div>
